---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Custom Dental Crowns in Footscray | Restore and Protect Your Teeth"
  description="At Top Dentists Footscray, we provide custom dental crowns to restore the function and appearance of damaged teeth. Our durable crowns are designed to blend seamlessly with your natural teeth, offering long-lasting protection and a confident smile."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Crowns</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Dental Crowns
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              A crown is a covering placed over the top of your own natural tooth to restore it for both function and appearance. Crowns will greatly enhance the look of heavily filled, chipped, discolored or irregular shaped teeth.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Crowns are an ideal way to rebuild teeth which have been broken, or have been weakened by decay or a very large filling. The crown fits right over the remaining part of the tooth, making it strong and giving it the shape and contour of a natural tooth.
            </p>

            <!-- When Crowns are Needed -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                When Are Crowns Recommended?
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Heavily filled teeth</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  When a tooth has large fillings that compromise its structural integrity, a crown provides comprehensive protection.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Broken or fractured teeth</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Teeth that have been damaged by trauma or wear can be rebuilt and strengthened with crowns.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>After root canal treatment</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Teeth that have undergone root canal therapy often require crowns to restore their strength and appearance.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Cosmetic enhancement</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Crowns can improve the appearance of discolored, irregularly shaped, or misaligned teeth.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Crown Materials -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Crown Materials We Offer
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Porcelain</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Natural appearance, excellent for front teeth</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Porcelain-fused-to-metal</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Strong and durable with good aesthetics</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Ceramic</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Metal-free option with superior aesthetics</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Zirconia</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Extremely strong and naturally colored</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Crown Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                The Crown Procedure
              </h3>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">First Visit:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Tooth preparation and shaping</li>
                    <li>• Digital impressions or molds</li>
                    <li>• Temporary crown placement</li>
                    <li>• Color matching for natural appearance</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Second Visit:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Temporary crown removal</li>
                    <li>• Permanent crown fitting</li>
                    <li>• Bite adjustment and refinement</li>
                    <li>• Final cementation</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits of Crowns -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Benefits of Dental Crowns
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Protection</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Shields weakened teeth</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Strength</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Restores full function</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Aesthetics</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Natural appearance</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Crown Care -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Caring for Your Crown
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Brush and floss regularly</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Avoid chewing hard objects</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Use a nightguard if you grind teeth</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Regular dental check-ups</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Crown Longevity
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    10-15 years or more
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    With proper care and regular dental visits, crowns can provide long-lasting protection and aesthetics.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Restore Your Teeth with Custom Crowns
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Strengthen and beautify damaged teeth. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          to learn about crown options
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>